Use the trick George knows to grab it with the little possible moves.

Look ahead, count your steps and catch the monkey right now before it runs away. It is very fast, so you need to be very alter to make the job done in this brand new adventure game. Put your best and help George to grab his favorite monkeys soon. Once it Is done, he will also teach you how to catch the tigers. You are definitely having a lot of fun and interests in this one of the best adventure games for boys. Use your mind to control 2 characters at the same time in this new HTML5 game.

With seamless gameplay, easy control, excellent graphics and awesome audio and video effects, Monkeeper features 24 levels and approximately 1 hour of gameplay. Once you explore its various levels, you are sure to try this cool puzzle game again and again in your browser. Play it in your PC using keyword or mobile phone with the help of smooth touches. Move blocks when required and find out the perfect combination of moves to make your win in the end! All the best kids!
